      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm working on a shopify theme and the product page is acting weird on mobile. the product image is overlapping the title text on iphone screens specifically. i tried adjusting the padding but it didnt help. here is the css for the product header section:\n\n.product-header {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  padding: 20px;\n}\n\n.product-media {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n}\n\n.product-info {\n  margin-top: -10px;\n}\n\nany idea why the image is bleeding into the text area on smaller screens?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey so i'm working on a shopify theme and the product page is acting weird on mobile. the product image is overlapping the title text on iphone screens specifically. i tried adjusting the padding but it didnt help. here is the css for the product header section:\n\n.product-header {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  padding: 20px;\n}\n\n.product-media {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n}\n\n.product-info {\n  margin-top: -10px;\n}\n\nany idea why the image is bleeding into the text area on smaller screens?",
